        <h1>CollegeCupid IITG - Policy Against Child Sexual Abuse & Exploitation</h1>
        <p>At <strong>SWC IITG</strong>, we are committed to preventing <strong>child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE)</strong> on our platform. We strictly prohibit any content, behavior, or activities that involve the sexual abuse, exploitation, or endangerment of minors.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Commitments</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>We <strong>do not allow</strong> any content that depicts, promotes, or facilitates CSAE.</li>
            <li>Any such content will be <strong>immediately removed</strong>, and the user responsible will be banned.</li>
            <li>We actively <strong>monitor and moderate</strong> content for CSAE violations.</li>
            <li>We comply with <strong>local laws and law enforcement agencies</strong> in investigating any CSAE-related reports.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How We Prevent CSAE</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Strict <strong>content moderation policies</strong> and AI-based detection.</li>
            <li>User <strong>reporting system</strong> for CSAE violations.</li>
            <li>Regular <strong>review of content</strong> to ensure compliance.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Reporting CSAE Violations</h2>
        <p>If you encounter any CSAE-related content, please report it immediately via:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:swc@iitg.ac.in">swc@iitg.ac.in</a></li>
            <li>In-app reporting system</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We are dedicated to <strong>creating a safe digital environment</strong> for all users.</p>
        
